                        h2 Cabo Azul Resort: A Masterpiece of Oceanfront Luxury and Architectural Grandeur
                        h3 Prime Shoreline Position in San José del Cabo
                        p Cabo Azul Resort occupies a commanding beachfront position in San José del Cabo, offering breathtaking panoramas of the Sea of Cortez and direct access to the region’s most picturesque coastline.
                        p Nestled just moments from the historic heart of the city, the resort serves as an elegant gateway to the legendary Art District, where colonial charm meets contemporary galleries and world-class gastronomy. Located only 20 minutes from Los Cabos International Airport (SJD), the property offers an effortless transition into a world of sophisticated relaxation.
                        p This sanctuary provides a refined and tranquil alternative to the high-energy pace of Cabo San Lucas, while remaining within easy reach of championship golf courses, elite marinas, and the captivating desert adventures of Baja.

        section.features
            .container
                .row
                    .col-12
                        h3 Exquisite Suites and Hacienda-Inspired Design
                        p Renowned for its dramatic open-air architecture, Cabo Azul Resort is a villa-style retreat characterized by soaring archways, hand-painted artisanal tiles, and fire-lit water features. With approximately 320 meticulously appointed suites, it stands as one of the most prestigious large-scale luxury resorts in the area.
                        p Our accommodations range from intimate junior suites to expansive one, two, and three-bedroom villas, each designed as a private residential sanctuary featuring:
                        ul
                            li Private balconies or terraces designed for coastal lounging
                            li Sophisticated kitchenettes or fully equipped gourmet kitchens
                            li Expansive living and dining salons in premium villas
                            li Spa-inspired bathrooms with deep soaking tubs and rainfall showers
                            li Integrated smart technology and high-speed connectivity
                            li In-suite laundry facilities in select luxury categories

                        p The interior design seamlessly marries traditional Mexican craftsmanship with modern opulence, creating an ambiance that is both majestic and welcoming.

                        h3 World-Class Resort Amenities
                        p The Cabo Azul experience is defined by an extensive collection of lifestyle amenities:
                        ul
                            li A dramatic central complex of oceanfront infinity-edge pools
                            li Signature swim-up bars and exclusive poolside cabanas
                            li A serene full-service spa and wellness sanctuary
                            li State-of-the-art fitness and conditioning center
                            li Acclaimed on-site fine dining and chic lounge areas
                            li 24-hour personalized concierge and professional security

                        p The resort’s iconic tri-level infinity pool, framed by majestic arches against the azure horizon, remains one of the most celebrated architectural sights in Los Cabos.

                        h3 A Destination for Discerning Travelers
                        p With its spacious residential layouts, Cabo Azul Resort is the premier choice for multi-generational families, romantic celebrations, and group retreats. By balancing architectural beauty with world-class hospitality, it offers a transcendent luxury experience in the heart of San José del Cabo.

